name: Free Hispter Vectors
description:

You will find 12 ready-to-use Logos with color variations and 12 icons perfect for adorning different commercial products and businesses such as stores, marketing, restaurants or products.

- Easy to edit and change colors

- Icons are scalable to any size you need (vectorized)

- Easy to use for developers


Getting the premium pack you will get:


- 160 Logos

- 40 Posters
